data.description: Ready for a move-in ready home in an awesome neighborhood, excellent schools, & private back yard (no neighbors behind you). You will appreciate additional features added by owners since 2018 new up-grade build which include a lge back patio, fresh paint inside, private fenced backyard w raised garden area,& new LPV flooring recently installed on upper level. Main living areas are also LPV & tile. No carpet here & relief for allergy sensitive folks! Level 1 bedroom w ensuite bath is currently used as a home office. Kitchen features black cabinets, granite counters, double gas oven. A lofty dining area opens to the kitchen, w additional granite bar seating making the space for hosting a crowd. Living room is designed for gathering & lounging & extra cozy because of the fireplace. Really comfortable & casual. The main level also has a half bath & a step out patio! Take the Party Outside with this extended entertaining space.
